    <dialogue id="Intro">
        <text>
        After opening a strange book inside a bookstore you find yourself at Hell's doorstep
        reading a weird paper sign that reads:

      ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
      │ HELP!! Whoever reads this, I hope you are stronger than all of those who came before │
      │  you because you now have to get to Lucifer and rid him of the 'Heart of the Abyss', │
      │  a magical rock that gives control over the Abyssal power and turns its bearer into  │
      │     Hell's Sovereign, otherwise all souls will be doomed to suffer for eternity!     │
      │      And REMEMBER, the more Sins you carry the greater the chances are that you      │
      │                                   DO NOT SURVIVE!                                    │
      └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

        You think for a moment before opening the old metal gate and walking inside...

        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>Phrase</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="Phrase">
        <text>
        In the depths of despair, where souls linger and sins fester, your journey through
        the Inferno begins. Will you seek redemption or embrace the darkness?
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>1</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
