        After walking for a while and crossing the second circle you reach the entrance to the
        third circle of Hell, Gluttony. You travel across it until you see a new entrance in
        the distance, but all of a sudden Cerberus appears and blocks your path.
        What will you do?
        </text>
        <options>
            <option description="Attack Cerberus, getting an object that might be helpful later on." nextDialogueId="cerberusBattle" />
            <option description="Try to win Cerberus over so he lets you go." nextDialogueId="8" alternativeNextId="9"  reward="5 Sins"/>
            <option description="Try to run away and get through another route." nextDialogueId="10" alternativeNextId="11"  reward="15 Sins"/>
        </options>
    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="8">
        <text>
        You see a huge bone a few meters from you and decide to throw it to him.
        Unsurprisingly he runs to catch it, and you proceed to run towards the entrance to the
        next circle. You get 5 Sin points.
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>12</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="9">
        <text>
        You can't find anything with which to win Cerberus over or distract him with,
        he runs towards you and eats you.
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>DEATH</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="10">
        <text>
        You got away from Cerberus before he could see you and found an alternative route,
        but it's so long that you have tons of time to think about your Sins and their weight
        on your back. You get 15 Sin points.
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>12</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="11">
        <text>
        You try to run away from Cerberus, but he's faster than you, catches you and eats you.
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>DEATH</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
