    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="13">
        <text>
        Aquiles enrages but when he tries to get you, you dodge him, and he hits his head
        on a wall. While he recovers you make your escape.
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>15</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
