        After the encounter you keep walking until you get to the next circle of Hell, Heresy.
        There you see tons of tombs on fire, where Epicurus and his followers are trapped,
        he offers to give you a forbidden power if you let go of your faith and pry open
        the flaming tomb in which he is trapped.
        </text>
        <options>
            <option description="Accept the offer letting go of your faith and helping him." nextDialogueId="16" reward="The Heresy Knowledge"/>
            <option description="Reject the offer and try to continue." nextDialogueId="demonBattle"/>
        </options>
    </dialogue>
    <dialogue id="16">
        <text>
        Epicurus gives you a wand he calls 'The Heresy Knowledge', with which you can find
        out an opponent's weakness and use it against them, and you go on with you journey.
        </text>
        <nextDialogueId>17</nextDialogueId>
    </dialogue>
