        You find Odysseus, who tells you that if you throw a soul to the river of lost souls
        he will teach you the arts of deceit.
        </text>
        <options>
            <option description="Accept the offer throwing a soul to the river of lost souls, making it suffer for eternity." nextDialogueId="21" reward="Circe's Gloves"/>
            <option description="Reject the offer and try to continue." nextDialogueId="odysseusBattle"/>
        </options>
    </dialogue>
